545/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-3894440.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=December 10, 2017|title=Springsteen going over Berlin Wall|date=July 13, 1988|work=[[Chicago Sun-Times]]|accessdate=December 9, 2017}}</ref>\n\n|-\n| September 20, 1997\n!scope=\"row\"| [[U2]]\n| Aeroporto di Reggio Emilia\n| [[Reggio Emilia]]\n| [[PopMart Tour]]\n| {{nts|150,000}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/photos/u2-the-ultimate-music-guide-on-sale-now-1434012|title='U2: The Ultimate Music Guide' \u2013 on sale now - NME|date=April 29, 2009|website=NME|accessdate=December 9, 2017}}</ref>\n\n|-\n| March 20, 1981\n!scope=\"row\"| [[Queen (band)|Queen]]\n| [[Est\u00e1dio do Morumbi]]\n| [[S\u00e3o Paulo]]\n| [[The Game Tour]]\n| {{nts|131,000}}\n| <ref name=\"Henke\">{{cite magazine |last=Henke |first=James |work=[[Rolling Stone]] |date=June 11, 1981 |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/news/story/23501689/queen_holds_court_in_south_america/print |title=Queen Holds Court in South America|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090909113253/https://www.rollingstone.com/news/story/23501689/queen_holds_court_in_south_america/print|archivedate=September 9, 2009}}</ref>\n\n|-\n| August 29, 1987\n!scope=\"row\"| [[Madonna (entertainer)|Madonna]]\n| [[Sceaux, Hauts-de-Seine|Parc de Sceaux]]\n| Paris\n| [[Who's That Girl World Tour]]\n| {{nts|130,000}}\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.elpais.com/articulo/cultura/MADONNA_/ACTRIZ/MuSICA/SOLLERS/_PHILIPPE/FRANCIA/Madonna/convoco/Paris/130/000/personas/culminacion/gira/europea/elpepicul/19870831elpepicul_10/Tes|title=Madonna convoc\u00f3 en Par\u00eds a 130.000 personas|language=Spanish|accessdate=May 4, 2009|work=[[El Pa\u00eds]]|location=Madrid|publisher=[[Jes\u00fas de Polanco]]|last=Bassets|first=Luis|date=August 31, 1987}}</ref>\n\n|-\n| August 5, 1995\n!scope=\"row\"| [[The Rolling Stones]]\n| [[Strahov Stadium]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Voodoo Lounge Tour]]\n| {{nts|126,742}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.americanradiohistory.com/A