{"title_page": "1935\u201336 Slovenian Republic League", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2013}}\n{{Infobox football league season\n| competition = [[Slovenian Republic League]]\n| season = 1935\u201336\n| winners = [[SK Ljubljana]]\n| total goals = 243\n| prevseason = [[1934\u201335 Slovenian Republic League|1934\u201335]]\n| nextseason = [[1936\u201337 Slovenian Republic League|1936\u201337]]\n}}\n\nThe '''1935\u201336 Slovenian Republic League''' was the 17th season of the [[Slovenian Republic Football League|Slovenian Republic League]]. [[SK Ljubljana]] had won the league for the first time.<ref name=\"league\">{{cite web | url = http://www.mnzveza-mb.si/datoteke/e-katalog/index.html | title = MNZ Maribor - 80 let nogometa v Mariboru |trans-title=80 years of football in Maribor| publisher = MNZ Maribor | year = 2008 | accessdate = 14 August 2013 | language = Slovenian }}</ref>\n\n==Ljubljana subdivision==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n|sortable_table=y\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=PRI|name_PRI=[[A\u0160K Primorje|Primorje]]\n|team2=HER|name_HER=[[\u017dSK Hermes|Hermes]]\n|team3=CEL|name_CEL=[[NK Celje|Celje]]\n|team4=KOR|name_KOR=[[NK Triglav Kranj (defunct)|Korotan]]\n|team5=ILI|name_ILI=[[ND Ilirija Ljubljana|Ilirija]]\n|win_PRI=7|draw_PRI=1|loss_PRI=0|gf_PRI=32|ga_PRI=8\n|win_HER=6|draw_HER=1|loss_HER=1|gf_HER=30|ga_HER=9\n|win_CEL=3|draw_CEL=1|loss_CEL=4|gf_CEL=11|ga_CEL=22\n|win_KOR=2|draw_KOR=1|loss_KOR=5|gf_KOR=16|ga_KOR=29\n|win_ILI=0|draw_ILI=0|loss_ILI=8|gf_ILI=0|ga_ILI=21\n\n|col_C=green1|text_C=\n|result1=C|result2=C\n|col_R=red1|text_R=\n|result5=R\n|update=complete|source=\n}}\n\n==Maribor subdivision==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|sortable_table=y\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=MRB|name_MRB=[[NK \u017delezni\u010dar Maribor|\u017delezni\u010dar Maribor]]\n|team2=\u010cAK|name_\u010cAK=[[NK \u010cakovec|\u010cakovec]]\n|team3=SSK|name_SSK=[[I. SSK Maribor]]\n|team4=ATH|name_ATH=[[SK Cillier 