an Republic League''' was the 17th season of the [[Slovenian Republic Football League|Slovenian Republic League]]. [[SK Ljubljana]] had won the league for the first time.<ref name=\"league\">{{cite web | url = http://www.mnzveza-mb.si/datoteke/e-katalog/index.html | title = MNZ Maribor - 80 let nogometa v Mariboru |trans-title=80 years of football in Maribor| publisher = MNZ Maribor | year = 2008 | accessdate = 14 August 2013 | language = Slovenian }}</ref>\n\n==Ljubljana subdivision==\n{{fb cl header|sort=y|noqr=y}}\n|-style=\"background: #90EE90;\"\n| 1 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[A\u0160K Primorje|Primorje]] || 8 || 7 || 1 || 0 || 32 || 8 || +24 || '''15'''\n|-style=\"background: #90EE90;\"\n| 2 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[\u017dSK Hermes|Hermes]] || 8 || 6 || 1 || 1 || 30 || 9 || +21 || '''13'''\n|-\n| 3 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[NK Celje|Celje]] || 8 || 3 || 1 || 4 || 11 || 22 || \u201311 || '''7'''\n|-\n| 4 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[NK Triglav Kranj (defunct)|Korotan]] || 8 || 2 || 1 || 5 || 16 || 29 || \u201313 || '''5'''\n|-style=\"background:#FF6666\"\n| 5 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[ND Ilirija Ljubljana|Ilirija]] || 8 || 0 || 0 || 8 || 0 || 21 || \u201321 || '''0'''\n|}\n\n==Maribor subdivision==\n{{fb cl header|sort=y|noqr=y}}\n|-style=\"background: #90EE90;\"\n| 1 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[NK \u017delezni\u010dar Maribor|\u017delezni\u010dar Maribor]] || 8 || 6 || 1 || 1 || 22 || 11 || +11 || '''13'''\n|-style=\"background: #90EE90;\"\n| 2 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[NK \u010cakovec|\u010cakovec]] || 8 || 4 || 1 || 3 || 22 || 18 || +4 || '''9'''\n|-\n| 3 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[I. SSK Maribor]] || 8 || 4 || 1 || 3 || 28 || 24 || +4 || '''9'''\n|-\n| 4 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[SK Cillier Athletik|Athletik]] || 8 || 3 || 0 || 5 || 15 || 30 || \u201315 || '''6'''\n|-\n| 5 ||style=\"text-align:left\"|[[SV Rapid Marburg|Rapid]] || 8 || 1 || 1 || 6 || 19 || 22 || \u20133 || '''3'''\n|}\n\n==Final==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\